{"tid":874220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[港足揀蟀飛台] 戴偉浚再度入選! 或領銜港隊十一月鬥北韓","createTime":"2018-10-24T04:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T15:31:12.000Z","uid":9030,"like":2,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"402a74456729432bf54fc7fbc8a3bc4567fb0e25","tid":874220,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"【香港，2018年10月24日】：香港代表隊將參與在本年十一月在台北展開的EAFF E-1東亞足球錦標賽2019第二圈賽事。香港代表隊會於2018年11月11日、13日及16日進行三場比賽。決選名單將於「中銀人壽香港超級聯賽」第六週比賽後公佈。球隊現在公佈三十人初選名單和訓練時間表。<br />\n<br />\n守門員<br />\n陳嘉豪 (佳聯元朗) 、葉鴻輝 (東方龍獅)、王振鵬 (傑志)、袁皓俊 (理文)<br />\n<br />\n後衛<br />\n霍斌仁 (維塞烏學院足球會)、鄭璟昊、曾錦濤、黃梓浩 (東方龍獅)、<br />\n法圖斯 (貴州恒豐)、丹 尼、列斯奧、唐建文 (傑志)、劉學銘 (冠忠南區)、<br />\n羅 素 (遼寧宏運)、徐宏傑 (梅州客家)、梁諾恆 (富力R&amp;F)<br />\n<br />\n中場<br />\n梁振邦、徐德帥、茹子楠 (東方龍獅)、黃 洋 (傑志)、戴偉浚 (牛津聯)<br />\n陳俊樂 (富力R&amp;F)、鍾偉強、李嘉耀、黃 威 (和富大埔)<br />\n<br />\n前鋒<br />\n麥 基 (東方龍獅)、辛 祖 (PSM望加錫)、基奧雲尼 (富力R&amp;F)、<br />\n基 奧 (新疆天山雪豹)、艾力士 (延邊富德)"},{"pid":"44accf7d0c8a897fae5b1f96eb421e478f8b47c1","tid":874220,"uid":9030,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"GW係咪想逼死Tsun Dai<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c8fcd01fa48bda5b185fa333e3671866b08cd7","tid":874220,"uid":33605,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"猶戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2573a635f4d1f35878925b3987edd1e632bcdbea","tid":874220,"uid":60281,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZELMV0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZELMV0q.jpg&h=d2548e2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"509053ef1d88fe973cb85ce55d506dca9056dd34","tid":874220,"uid":37528,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-